<plot>This Columbia short (Columbia production number 5802) finds Bill Stern at the Concord Hotel, in New York's Catskill Mountains, watching profession ice-skater Everett McGowan show off the skills that has him as speed-champ of ice-skating. McGowan's daughter performs a ballet on ice, and then joins George von Birgelen, who skates on stilts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?111239</url></doc>
